name: Cashlendernow
overview:
CashLenderNow is an online platform that connects you to a direct lender on the phone. We realize that emergencies arise from time to time, and people need emergency cash. Whether it is bills, groceries, or a much needed vacation,we can connect you to a direct lender in a matter of minutes to get you the cash you need.

No online forms to fill out, and no credit checks – just Call 1-888-718-1982, answer a few question with the press of a button, and get connected to a direct lender immediately!
